'From Squeak3.8beta of ''2 November 2004'' [latest update: #6374] on 21 November 2004 at 11:01:30 pm'!"Change Set:		KCPbecomeTestsDate:			21 November 2004Author:			stephane ducasseA nice test for becomeForward:"!!ObjectTest methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'sd 11/19/2004 17:19'!testBecome	"self debug: #testBecome"	"this test should that all the variables pointing to an object are pointing now to another one.	Not that this inverse is not true. This kind of become is called oneWayBecome, while	VisualWorks become was symmetric"	| pt1 pt2 pt3 |	pt1 := 0@0.	pt2 := pt1.	pt3 := 100@100.	pt1 becomeForward: pt3.	self assert: (pt2 = (100@100)).	self assert: pt3 == pt2.	self assert: pt1 = (100@100)! !